This is a placeholder for KYC_Form.xlsx

In a real implementation, this would be an Excel file with the following structure:

Column Headers (Row 1):
- Full Name
- Date of Birth
- Address
- Phone Number
- Email Address
- PAN Number
- Aadhaar Number
- Company Name
- Job Title
- Annual Income
- Account Number
- IFSC Code

The form filler would extract data from documents and populate these fields automatically.
